<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 18:09:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加沙战争紧张局势扰乱校园；布朗抗议者被捕；哈弗福德大楼被占用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/gaza-war-tensions-roil-campuses-brown-protesters-arrested-haverford-building-occupied/0000018c-68ec-d798-adac-ecef866e0000</link><description>数十名学生因抗议以色列在加沙的行动而拒绝离开大学大楼而被捕，这是一个月内的第二轮逮捕</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 17:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/gaza-war-tensions-roil-campuses-brown-protesters-arrested-haverford-building-occupied/0000018c-68ec-d798-adac-ecef866e0000</guid></item><item><title>禁止暴力定居者：美国和欧洲制定拒绝入境者的标准</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/banning-violent-settlers-u-s-europe-formulating-criteria-on-who-will-be-refused-entry/0000018c-6914-db38-a9fc-e9b632200000</link><description>随着针对暴力以色列定居者的国际行动势头增强，美国、英国和欧盟正在寻找方法，对那些在西岸对巴勒斯坦人实施暴力的人实施和执行签证禁令和其他限制</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 16:45:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/banning-violent-settlers-u-s-europe-formulating-criteria-on-who-will-be-refused-entry/0000018c-6914-db38-a9fc-e9b632200000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡称10月7日的死亡人数与奥斯陆的死亡人数相同——更多的操纵和逃避责任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-oct-7-death-toll-equal-to-oslos-a-comparison-that-does-not-bode-well/0000018c-6819-dbd5-a39c-ff7b56f20000</link><description>总理没有详细说明他的说法背后的计算，但进一步的检查表明这些数据可以被操纵，并且需要背景。最重要的是，内塔尼亚胡在这里也至少承担部分责任</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 14:42:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-oct-7-death-toll-equal-to-oslos-a-comparison-that-does-not-bode-well/0000018c-6819-dbd5-a39c-ff7b56f20000</guid></item><item><title>备受争议的汉娜·阿伦特奖颁奖典礼被推迟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/controversial-award-ceremony-for-the-hannah-arendt-prize-postponed/0000018c-6893-d798-adac-ecbf6f560000</link><description>玛莎·格森因在美国杂志《纽约客》的一篇文章中发表言论而受到批评，据说他们在文中将加沙的局势与二战期间被占领的欧洲犹太人聚居区进行了比较</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 13:52:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/controversial-award-ceremony-for-the-hannah-arendt-prize-postponed/0000018c-6893-d798-adac-ecbf6f560000</guid></item><item><title>拜登以色列和乌克兰政策背后的价值观</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/the-values-behind-bidens-israel-and-ukraine-policies/0000018c-67f3-dbd5-a39c-fff3c7ee0000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登对乌克兰和加沙战争及危机的处理堪称典范，迄今为止也是成功的。两国都很幸运，这些战争发生在一位既是自由干涉主义者又是现实主义者的领导人的领导下</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 13:47:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/the-values-behind-bidens-israel-and-ukraine-policies/0000018c-67f3-dbd5-a39c-fff3c7ee0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军与杰宁武装分子交火，三名巴勒斯坦人丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/three-palestinians-killed-in-exchange-of-fire-between-idf-and-gunmen-in-jenin/0000018c-6857-de5e-a3ef-6bff5f9a0000</link><description>以色列士兵被拍摄到在难民营中使用清真寺扬声器向难民营居民发出呼吁，并唱光明节歌曲。以色列国防军表示，这些士兵立即被解除执行任务</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 13:32:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/three-palestinians-killed-in-exchange-of-fire-between-idf-and-gunmen-in-jenin/0000018c-6857-de5e-a3ef-6bff5f9a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列批准2023年补充战时预算</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israel-approves-supplementary-wartime-budget-for-2023/0000018c-6838-de5e-a3ef-6bfd79920000</link><description>该修正案以 58 票赞成、44 票反对的投票结果获得批准。内塔尼亚胡领导的利库德集团情报部长吉拉·加姆利尔缺席投票，利库德集团议员尤利·埃德尔斯坦最初投了赞成票，但后来要求修改投票以弃权。</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 12:22:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israel-approves-supplementary-wartime-budget-for-2023/0000018c-6838-de5e-a3ef-6bfd79920000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯高级官员建议遵循巴解组织官方立场承认以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/top-hamas-official-suggests-recognizing-israel-following-official-plo-stance/0000018c-67e4-d798-adac-e7ef81fd0000</link><description>目前尚不清楚阿布·马祖克在接受​​《中东观察报》采访时所表达的立场是否代表了该组织的立场。他还为哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击辩护，并表示这实现了该组织的目标：“每个人都在谈论巴勒斯坦事业”</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 11:26:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/top-hamas-official-suggests-recognizing-israel-following-official-plo-stance/0000018c-67e4-d798-adac-e7ef81fd0000</guid></item><item><title>哈大沙妇女组织谴责红十字会未能救治被哈马斯扣押在加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/hadassah-women-group-slams-red-cross-failure-to-treat-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018c-67b3-de43-affd-f7b3080a0000</link><description>美国妇女犹太复国主义组织哈大沙致信正在访问以色列的红十字会主席：“红十字会以前是否曾以如此公然的方式未能照顾人质和武装侵略的受害者，或者这种待遇是保留的吗？”对于从以色列被绑架的人？</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 10:44:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/hadassah-women-group-slams-red-cross-failure-to-treat-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018c-67b3-de43-affd-f7b3080a0000</guid></item><item><title>对加沙泥潭的担忧：以色列是否陷入另一场长期消耗战？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/fears-of-a-gaza-quagmire-is-israel-in-another-long-war-of-attrition/0000018c-6322-d798-adac-e7af94c90000</link><description>政治和军事层面幻想一场长期战争，却没有任何结束计划，忽视人质，并相信公众已经习惯了军事损失</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 10:32:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/fears-of-a-gaza-quagmire-is-israel-in-another-long-war-of-attrition/0000018c-6322-d798-adac-e7af94c90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名周三在加沙战斗中丧生的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israeli-army-names-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting-on-wednesday/0000018c-674f-de43-affd-f74ffe910000</link><description>周三，来自哈里什的 38 岁军士长伊莱沙·莱文施滕 (Elisha Levinshtern) 在加沙地带南部被反坦克导弹击中身亡。莱文施滕身后留下了他的妻子哈达斯和他的六个孩子</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 08:23:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israeli-army-names-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting-on-wednesday/0000018c-674f-de43-affd-f74ffe910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长告诉美国国家安全顾问，击败哈马斯将需要“几个月以上的时间”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article-live/hostages-families-demand-clarification-from-netanyahu-over-decision-not-to-hold-talks/0000018c-65b5-de43-affd-f5b7d6250000</link><description>人质家属要求“立即澄清”战时内阁决定暂停摩萨德主席计划前往卡塔尔重启谈判的决定 ■ 以色列人据信被绑架，10 月 7 日被发现被谋杀 ■ 坦桑尼亚国民也被发现被杀 ■ 美国认为现阶段停止战争“不符合该地区所有人的长期安全利益” ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生；超过 138 名人质仍被扣押在加沙 ■ 哈马斯卫生部称加沙有 18,608 人死亡、50,594 人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 04:07:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article-live/hostages-families-demand-clarification-from-netanyahu-over-decision-not-to-hold-talks/0000018c-65b5-de43-affd-f5b7d6250000</guid></item><item><title>舒贾耶战役暴露了以色列军队的缺陷，但并不表明加沙战斗发生了变化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/hamas-knows-us-better-than-we-do/0000018c-64cf-d798-adac-e4ef2dc40000</link><description>以色列军队从未在人口稠密的城市地区经历过如此长时间的战斗，因此尚无法宣布控制加沙地带北部。然而，战斗性质的真正改变不是由哈马斯带来的，而是由美国加大压力带来的</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 04:03:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/hamas-knows-us-better-than-we-do/0000018c-64cf-d798-adac-e4ef2dc40000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔的部门运作“就像一个犯罪组织接管了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-ministry-runs-like-a-crime-organization-has-taken-over/0000018c-650f-d798-adac-e5af492e0000</link><description>消息人士称，安全部长对他的员工感到恐惧，并不断干扰他们的工作以促进他的政治利益。另一位消息人士称，他周围都是高级警官，以提升自己的公众形象，并且“痴迷于媒体”</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 04:03:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-ministry-runs-like-a-crime-organization-has-taken-over/0000018c-650f-d798-adac-e5af492e0000</guid></item><item><title>降雨迫使加沙人离开临时营地，增加了疾病风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/rain-forces-gazans-out-of-makeshift-camps-increases-risk-of-disease/0000018c-650e-d798-adac-e5afa6bc0000</link><description>加沙南部流离失所的巴勒斯坦人营地的洪水加剧了本已严重的人道主义危机，影响了数万家庭。更令人担忧的是近东救济工程处和其他援助组织显然无力提供援助</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 23:22:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/rain-forces-gazans-out-of-makeshift-camps-increases-risk-of-disease/0000018c-650e-d798-adac-e5afa6bc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战时内阁阻止摩萨德主席在卡塔尔重启人质谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-cabinet-blocks-mossad-chief-from-restarting-hostage-talks-in-qatar/0000018c-64ee-dbd5-a39c-ffffefd60000</link><description>以色列战时内阁决定不提出新协议框架，怀疑卡塔尔谈判是否有效</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 21:18:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-cabinet-blocks-mossad-chief-from-restarting-hostage-talks-in-qatar/0000018c-64ee-dbd5-a39c-ffffefd60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院规定，改革派和保守派皈依者有资格获得包皮环切术的全额资助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/reform-conservative-converts-qualify-for-subsidized-circumcisions-top-israeli-court-says/0000018c-63c3-d798-adac-e7ef22640000</link><description>经过十多年的努力，高等法院本周决定，在拉比批准的州皈依计划之外的皈依者也必须获得国家对程序的援助</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 18:25:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/reform-conservative-converts-qualify-for-subsidized-circumcisions-top-israeli-court-says/0000018c-63c3-d798-adac-e7ef22640000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装在以色列经济战中开辟了新的危险战线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/houthis-open-new-and-dangerous-front-in-israels-economic-war/0000018c-63a6-dbd5-a39c-fff75c430000</link><description>对与以色列有联系的船只的袭击威胁到以色列进出口的主要路线。对以色列来说幸运的是，红海的全球贸易也面临风险</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 18:06:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/houthis-open-new-and-dangerous-front-in-israels-economic-war/0000018c-63a6-dbd5-a39c-fff75c430000</guid></item><item><title>美国并未经历反以色列浪潮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/america-is-not-experiencing-an-anti-israel-tidal-wave/0000018c-6333-d6f9-afbc-7f7b36770000</link><description>以色列人痴迷于美国对加沙哈马斯战争的反应，许多人认为，由于这场冲突，美国人正在背叛他们的老盟友。对最近调查的分析表明情况更加复杂</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 17:44:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-13/ty-article/.premium/america-is-not-experiencing-an-anti-israel-tidal-wave/0000018c-6333-d6f9-afbc-7f7b36770000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列人看不到来自加沙的图像，因为我们的记者没有尽职尽责”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-12-13/ty-article-podcast/israelis-dont-see-images-from-gaza-because-our-journalists-are-not-doing-their-job/0000018c-5e34-de43-affd-fe36d3a70000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Dec 2023 16:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-12-13/ty-article-podcast/israelis-dont-see-images-from-gaza-because-our-journalists-are-not-doing-their-job/0000018c-5e34-de43-affd-fe36d3a70000</guid></item></channel></rss>